<white>synopsys:</>
    the comand <green>man</> is used to display the manual page about
    a command.
    
<white>usage: </><green>man</> <yellow>$command</>

<white>arguments:</>
    <yellow>$command</> - the name of the command.

<white>examples:</>
    <green>man</> <yellow>ls</>, <green>man</> <yellow>use</>, <green>man</> <yellow>rm</>